When editing stepfiles in freecad. 

Freecad as .deb package, install : $ sudo dpkg -i freecad.deb
https://github.com/grotius-cnc/Linux-Pro/releases/download/1.0.0/freecad.deb

For exporting seperate machine joints, create a compounnd of the selected joint. Then export the selected compound(s) as stepfile.
This will save the current solid position as it is.

![export_compounds_stepfile](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/44880102/139885192-cba49823-dc88-4f32-8465-5b55fe2e9564.jpg)
